---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Jona Gotthardt"
	description="That i am!"
	pubDate={new Date('August 12 2025')}
	heroImage="/mc1.jpg"
>
	<style>
		body {
			margin: 0;
			font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
			color: #e0e0e0;
			overflow-x: hidden;
			background: radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom, #0a0a0a 0%, #000000 100%);
		}

		/* Sterne-Hintergrund */
		body::before {
			content: "";
			position: fixed;
			top: 0;
			left: 0;
			width: 100%;
			height: 100%;
			background: url('/stars.png') repeat;
			background-size: cover;
			opacity: 0.3;
			z-index: -1;
			animation: starMove 200s linear infinite;
		}

		@keyframes starMove {
			from { background-position: 0 0; }
			to { background-position: -10000px 5000px; }
		}

		h1, h2, h3 {
			color: #00bcd4;
			text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,188,212,0.5);
		}

		p, li {
			color: #f0f0f0;
		}

		ul li::before {
			content: "✔";
			margin-right: 10px;
			color: #00bcd4;
		}

		code {
			background: rgba(0,188,212,0.1);
			padding: 3px 6px;
			border-radius: 5px;
			color: #00bcd4;
		}

		a.discord-btn {
			display: inline-block;
			margin-top: 20px;
			padding: 15px 40px;
			border-radius: 15px;
			background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00bcd4, #ff4081);
			color: white;
			font-weight: bold;
			text-decoration: none;
			font-size: 1.2rem;
			box-shadow: 0 0 20px #00bcd499, 0 0 40px #ff408166;
			transition: all 0.4s ease;
		}

		a.discord-btn:hover {
			transform: scale(1.05);
			box-shadow: 0 0 30px #00bcd4aa, 0 0 60px #ff4081aa;
		}

		section {
			background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
			border-radius: 12px;
			padding: 30px;
			margin: 40px auto;
			max-width: 900px;
			transition: all 0.6s ease;
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateY(50px);
		}

		section.visible {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: translateY(0);
		}

		.hero-image {
			width: 100%;
			max-height: 400px;
			object-fit: cover;
			border-radius: 12px;
			margin-bottom: 30px;
			box-shadow: 0 0 40px #00bcd499;
			transform: translateY(0px);
			transition: transform 0.5s ease, box-shadow 0.5s ease;
		}
	</style>

	<!-- Hero Image -->
	<img src="/mc1.jpg" alt="CommunitySMP Hero" class="hero-image" id="heroImage" />

	<section>
	<p class="emoji-title">👋 <strong>About Me</strong></p>
	<p>
		Hi, I’m <strong>Jona Gotthardt</strong> – a developer and tech enthusiast from Germany.
		I focus on working with Minecraft systems, modding, and performance optimization.
	</p>
	<p>
		What started with simple servers and small projects turned into a deeper interest
		in how things actually work behind the scenes – from memory usage to custom systems.
	</p>
</section>

<section>
	<h3>What I Do</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Developing Minecraft mods and custom features</li>
		<li>Performance optimization (client & server)</li>
		<li>Testing and experimenting with systems</li>
		<li>Working with tools and automation</li>
	</ul>
</section>

<section>
	<h3>Projects</h3>
	<p>
		I work on different Minecraft-related projects, focusing on improving gameplay,
		performance, and stability through custom solutions.
	</p>
	<p>
		Most of my work is experimental – testing limits, building systems, and constantly
		improving things over time.
	</p>
</section>

<section>
	<h3>Background</h3>
	<p>
		I previously ran public Minecraft servers, but I’ve shifted my focus towards development
		and technical work instead.
	</p>
	<p>
		My goal is to understand systems deeply and build better solutions, not just use them.
	</p>
</section>

<section>
	<p>
		This site will continue to evolve as I work on new projects and ideas.
	</p>
</section>

	<script>
		// Animate sections on scroll
		const observer = new IntersectionObserver(entries => {
			entries.forEach(entry => {
				if(entry.isIntersecting){
					entry.target.classList.add('visible');
				}
			});
		}, { threshold: 0.2 });

		document.querySelectorAll('section').forEach(section => observer.observe(section));

		// Hero Parallax & Glow effect
		const hero = document.getElementById('heroImage');
		window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
			const scrollPos = window.scrollY;
			hero.style.transform = `translateY(${scrollPos * 0.3}px)`;
			hero.style.boxShadow = `0 0 ${40 + scrollPos * 0.1}px #00bcd499`;
		});
	</script>
</Layout>
